{
  "$id": "qa-pass",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "schema",
    "task",
    "acceptance"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "schema": {
      "const": "qa-pass"
    },
    "task": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "acceptance": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "passed": {
          "type": "integer"
        },
        "failed": {
          "type": "integer"
        },
        "total": {
          "type": "integer"
        }
      }
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "next": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  },
  "_note": "文档形态;运行时校验为 src-tauri/src/services/nexus_verdict.rs 的必填字段轻量校验,两者须同步维护。qa-verdict 组合 id 在校验层按 schema 字段分派到 qa-pass/qa-fail。"
}